						               													<description>Pizza Express contains six themed party games, all different but all tasty, all good, and all healthy.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;'Presto!' is a game of speed and visual acuity in which we will compete to be the first to get the ingredients of the recipe, even taking them away from rivals.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;'Pizza Crush' is a spatial vision game in which we will try to get the ingredients for our recipe from a common matrix that will vary with each player's decisions.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;In 'Mamma mia!' we will have to be the fastest in assembling the pizza slice requested by customers.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;At 'Another slice, please' we will force our luck to be the first to deliver 5 correct orders to customers.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;'Oh sole mio!' encourages us to collect sets of ingredients and complete orders of different value to be the winner.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Finally, 'La ricetta de la nonna' will force us to squeeze our brain to remember grandmother's mythical pizza recipe amidst the constant sway of ingredients.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The six games that make up Pizza Express have a more complex version so that children and adults never get bored and always find a challenge to face.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
